news.title: a start of something new! kind of..
news.text: the launch of something new - mainux...
news.content:
the launch of something new - mainux. 

if you don't know, we've been in business since 2017 as our previous agency mainello montage. we worked with a variety of different clients, startups, and small to medium sized businesses offering everything from development to marketing. 

we decided we wanted to focus on user centric experiences and offer our clients the best in user experience and user interface design services as our primary focus. we made some changes to our team, and hired some new professionals who specialiaze more in brand identity, uxui, and top tier development to help amplify our quality of work by ten. 

we're excited to continue serving you under our new name, mainux.

text.paragraph: we took what was working well with the previous logo and refined its form to work on a broader scale of applications and sizes.

thanks to the new redesign, the users involved in the testing were blown away by the ease of use. fitbux is now able to leverage their great technology with a clean ui to help them on their multi million dollar raise to help scale their product.
post completion of the rebranded identity and web application, we built a mobile app to help users keep up with their financial plan and manage transactions.

content.heading: the solution
content.text:
we solved the UX issues by facilitating multiple user studies and testing before launching the final product. 

we helped develop their web and mobile platforms, ensuring cross platform capabilities for their users. 

their platform now gets over 100,000 visitors each month.

home.cta: lead branding and marketing agency specializing in the cannabis and lifestyle industries. we focus on defining the optimal user experience and building readymade brands, websites, applications, and a suite of elaborate marketing services for our clients.
home.services_text:
our name is a play on words of our design philosophy - get to the core of the users ideal experience, then create your company around it. we take on every project and problem with an open mind, curious spirit and without preconceived ideas.

we love crafting beautiful, smart and innovative work that is focused on a business goals and lifting up the cannabis industry as a whole. we do this across multiple touch points to help organizations achieve their goals.

content.heading: our services and capabilities
content.text: we love crafting beautiful, smart and inspired work that is focused on a business goals and their customers. we do this across multiple touch points to help organizations achieve their goals.

content.heading:
growth
marketing
content.text: marketing is our bread and butter, and something we only offer to our previous branding and UIUX clients. once we’ve built a foundation through brand strategy and identity, we’re able to build up a team specific to your companies needs to get your product or service to a large audience and build your tribe.

agency.heading: the point where art  and tech meet

content.quote: you have to start with the customer experience and work your way back to technology.

content.heading: our approach
content.text:
everything we do at mainux consists of providing solutions for intended users. this can be applied to products, business models, branding, and especially digital solutions.

we put the needs of the user at the center of everything we create, which is the most powerful way to start and finish each project.
